
1: start node server  
cd node --> npm install --> npm run start

2:start web server
cd web --> npm install --> npm run dev

PS: 
core folder is the global resource that will included in the full site by the nginx SSI module.
we can build the tool.min.js in core project. And tool.min.js will exposed a global Object in window
named: order_core_tool
how to include the fragment: <!--#include file="/global.html" -->



